---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Navbar } from '../sections/Navbar';
import { QuoteSection } from '../sections/QuoteSection';
import { FooterSection } from '../sections/FooterSection';
---

<Layout 
  title="Terms & Conditions - Double O Detailing"
  description="Read our terms and conditions for car detailing services. Information about pricing, deposits, booking policies, and service terms for Double O Detailing in Glasgow."
  canonical="https://doubleodetailing.co.uk/terms"
>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-neutral-100 font-figtree text-black text-sm leading-5 antialiased">
    <Navbar client:load />
    <main class="pt-0">
      <section class="relative bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat pt-28 pb-20 md:pt-36 md:pb-32" style="background-image: url('/gallery/WhatsApp Image 2026-02-02 at 11.18.23 PM (3).jpeg');">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/50"></div>
        <div class="relative max-w-[1204px] mx-auto px-5 md:px-8">
          <div class="box-border caret-transparent gap-x-4 flex flex-col gap-y-4 text-center">
            <div class="box-border caret-transparent flex blur-0 justify-center">
              <div class="box-border caret-transparent border border-white/30 px-3 py-1 rounded-[1000px] border-solid">
                <div class="font-medium box-border caret-transparent leading-[22px] text-white">
                  Legal
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="box-border caret-transparent blur-0 max-w-[680px] mx-auto">
              <h1 class="text-[44px] font-medium box-border caret-transparent tracking-[-1.44px] leading-[52px] md:text-7xl md:leading-[80px] text-white">
                Terms &{" "}
                <span class="text-[44px] box-border caret-transparent leading-[52px] font-figtree md:text-7xl md:leading-[80px]">
                  Conditions
                </span>
              </h1>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="box-border caret-transparent py-[60px] md:py-[100px]">
        <div class="box-border caret-transparent max-w-[1204px] mx-auto px-5 md:px-8">
          <div class="box-border caret-transparent max-w-[800px] mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold box-border caret-transparent mb-10 md:text-3xl font-cabinet uppercase tracking-tight text-center">
              Booking Information
            </h2>
            <div class="box-border caret-transparent space-y-8">
              <div class="box-border caret-transparent">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-medium box-border caret-transparent mb-3 md:text-2xl uppercase tracking-tight">
                  Bookings
                </h3>
                <p class="text-base box-border caret-transparent leading-6 text-neutral-700">
                  We require a 10% holding deposit to secure a booking, this will be reduced from your bill.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="box-border caret-transparent">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-medium box-border caret-transparent mb-3 md:text-2xl uppercase tracking-tight">
                  Cancellation Policy
                </h3>
                <p class="text-base box-border caret-transparent leading-6 text-neutral-700">
                  We request that you provide at least <strong>48 hours notice</strong> for you cancelling your booking. Otherwise the deposit will be non-refundable.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="box-border caret-transparent">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-medium box-border caret-transparent mb-3 md:text-2xl uppercase tracking-tight">
                  Payment & Receipts
                </h3>
                <p class="text-base box-border caret-transparent leading-6 text-neutral-700">
                  Payment can be settled upfront or at the time of service, and please inform us if you would like a copy of the invoice provided to your email address.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="box-border caret-transparent">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-medium box-border caret-transparent mb-3 md:text-2xl uppercase tracking-tight">
                  Time / Price
                </h3>
                <p class="text-base box-border caret-transparent leading-6 text-neutral-700">
                  All timings and prices for services are based on a standard level of job at hand. Certain jobs will require more time using more materials and labour, thus the price could reflect this to bring the car back to the required satisfaction and quality.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="box-border caret-transparent">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-medium box-border caret-transparent mb-3 md:text-2xl uppercase tracking-tight">
                  Social Media
                </h3>
                <p class="text-base box-border caret-transparent leading-6 text-neutral-700">
                  Please let us know if you consent to your car being featured on our social media platforms.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="box-border caret-transparent">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-medium box-border caret-transparent mb-3 md:text-2xl uppercase tracking-tight">
                  Belongings in Vehicle
                </h3>
                <p class="text-base box-border caret-transparent leading-6 text-neutral-700">
                  We would appreciate if you could remove your belongings prior to the beginning of all services.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="box-border caret-transparent">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-medium box-border caret-transparent mb-3 md:text-2xl uppercase tracking-tight">
                  Water + Power
                </h3>
                <p class="text-base box-border caret-transparent leading-6 text-neutral-700">
                  We have our own power and water supply, thus we can operate anywhere that is convenient to you.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <QuoteSection client:load showTerms={false} />
      <FooterSection client:load />
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>
